### Terminal features

Some escape sequences only work in terminals that support them. The `terminal_features` setting maps such a
feature to the terminal programs supporting it. Values are matched case-insensitively against the `TERM_PROGRAM`
environment variable (Windows Terminal is detected via `WT_SESSION`).

| Name       | Type       | Default              | Description                                                                                                     |
| ---------- | ---------- | -------------------- | --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| `progress` | `[]string` | `[Windows Terminal]` | terminals supporting OSC 9;4 progress sequences during `upgrade` and `font install`. An empty list disables them |

